  1462            * PUTBOX - Put tiles in box
  1463            ************************************************************
  1464            *  BL   @PUTBOX
  1465            *  DATA P0,P1,P2,P3
  1466            *  ...
  1467            *  DATA EOL
  1468            *-----------------------------------------------------------
  1469            *  P0HB = Upper left corner Y
  1470            *  P0LB = Upper left corner X
  1471            *  P1HB = Box height
  1472            *  P1LB = Box width
  1473            *  P2   = Pointer to length-byte prefixed string
  1474            *  P3HB = Repeat box A-times vertically
  1475            *  P3LB = Repeat box B-times horizontally
  1476            *-----------------------------------------------------------
  1477            *  Register usage
  1478            *  ; TMP0   = work copy of YX cursor position
  1479            *  ; TMP1HB = Width  of box + X
  1480            *  ; TMP2HB = Height of box + Y
  1481            *  ; TMP3   = Pointer to string
  1482            *  ; TMP4   = Counter for string
  1483            *  ; @WAUX1 = Box AB repeat count
  1484            *  ; @WAUX2 = Copy of R11
  1485            *  ; @WAUX3 = YX position for next diagonal box
  1486            *-----------------------------------------------------------
  1487            *  ; Only byte operations on TMP1HB & TMP2HB.  
  1488            *  ; LO bytes of TMP1 and TMP2 reserved for future use.
  1489            ********@*****@*********************@***********************
